---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<Layout
  title="Sponsor GDB-Engines Rankings"
  description="Sponsor a GDB-Engines Rankings page. Reach engineers, architects and data leaders evaluating graph databases each month."
  canonical="https://gdb-engines.com/sponsor/"
>
  <main class="sponsor-page">
    <h1>Sponsor GDB-Engines Rankings</h1>

    <p>GDB-Engines Rankings publishes monthly popularity boards covering ~130 graph databases across data model, query language, implementation language and license. They're read by engineers and architects deciding which graph technology to adopt.</p>

    <p>If you'd like to sponsor a ranking page — for example, the Cypher, RDF, or Rust board — get in touch and we'll arrange the details.</p>

    <p class="contact"><a href="mailto:sponsor@gdb-engines.com">sponsor@gdb-engines.com</a></p>

    <hr />

    <h2>What sponsorship looks like</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>A clearly-marked sponsor placement on the chosen ranking page.</li>
      <li>One-month or longer terms.</li>
      <li>The underlying ranking methodology and scores are never adjusted for sponsors.</li>
    </ul>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .sponsor-page { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6; padding-bottom: 0.25rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .contact { font-size: 1.05rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .contact a { color: #1971c2; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
  .contact a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  hr { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6; margin: 2rem 0; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.25rem; color: #495057; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
</style>
